{"tid":2499840,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"《鏗鏘集》編導蔡玉玲被控虛假陳述作車輛查冊 罪名成立","createTime":"2021-04-22T07:45:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T07:50:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"ff60f77c91af25f27216b409bbcb9ea6653274d0","tid":2499840,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:45:13.000Z","msg":"#Breaking: Journalist @Baochoy is convicted of making false statements while searching thru gov vehicle license database for an investigative report, ruled by Principal Magistrate Ivy Chui.<br />\nHuge Blow to #HongKong's #PressFreedom. Unprecedented conviction of press for such crime.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/phoebe_kongwy/status/1385137450322825218\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fphoebe_kongwy%2Fstatus%2F1385137450322825218&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnfaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=97580401\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fphoebe_kongwy%2Fstatus%2F1385137450322825218&h=fa1256ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/phoebe_kongwy/status/1385137450322825218</a>"},{"pid":"951e0f0603cfc7d4d8c8a0f2925e8110efc36c3a","tid":2499840,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:45:27.000Z","msg":"#西九龍裁判法院第一庭<br />\n#徐綺薇主任裁判官<br />\n#裁決  #新聞工作<br />\n<br />\n蔡玉玲(37) 香港電台《鏗鏘集》編導&nbsp; <br />\n<br />\n控罪：兩項明知而作出在要項上虛假的陳述<br />\n<br />\n14:38 開庭<br />\n14:50 徐官宣讀判詞中<br />\n15:25 仲未完<br />\n15:37 裁定 要項、虛假<br />\n<br />\n15:44 速報：被告罪名成立"},{"pid":"ba8475f8b7f062c17a46e12d9e0031184da5800d","tid":2499840,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:45:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15198\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15198&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnfaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=733b4d4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15198</a><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第一庭<br />\n#徐綺薇主任裁判官<br />\n#裁決  #新聞工作<br />\n<br />\n蔡玉玲(37) 香港電台《鏗鏘集》編導  <br />\n<br />\n控罪：兩項明知而作出在要項上虛假的陳述<br />\n<br />\n14:38 開庭<br />\n14:50 徐官宣讀判詞中<br />\n15:25 仲未完<br />\n15:37 裁定 要項、虛假<br />\n<br />\n15:44 速報：被告罪名成立"},{"pid":"bd18861150e8ee6d38fbd43dd6cd3ebc157fdd96","tid":2499840,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:45:55.000Z","msg":"幾時判刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"838dbce528277cf1e8be0c4145cd30fa42bc9a64","tid":2499840,"uid":259402,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:46:58.000Z","msg":"新聞自由 呵呵 <br />\n<br />\n日日咁搞 公關都搞唔掂 <br />\n<br />\n外國見到新聞自由都冇哂 都仲可以繼續做生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f05d42a6cdea156f0ab053eb82e8b9c4185970","tid":2499840,"uid":321059,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:47:04.000Z","msg":"預撚咗<br />\n即使判咗唔成立<br />\n律政屍實上訴至高院<br />\n最後都係會罪成"},{"pid":"889d2216d4113b682157d6ec2ffce67112adfe3e","tid":2499840,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:47:13.000Z","msg":"Thus, all elements of knowingly make a statement which is false are established. @Baochoy is convicted of both charge of knowingly make a statement which is false to obtain a certificate of vehicle particulars.<br />\n<br />\nNow entering mitigation.<br />\n<br />\n#BREAKING<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/galileocheng/status/1385137851453427717\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgalileocheng%2Fstatus%2F1385137851453427717&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnfaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=64c12112\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgalileocheng%2Fstatus%2F1385137851453427717&h=682eea6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/galileocheng/status/1385137851453427717</a>"},{"pid":"9ca0030343f36aa552d768aeaa